title: WHIRLING / MONEYMAN barks
description: A wildly succesful barking moneyman exclaims lots of comments about money.

dialogueTree.title: Moneyman: ""It's all about money, you know.""
Moneyman: ""You gotta spend money to make mone..."
dialogueTree.english: "You gotta spend money to make money."

dialogueTree.title: Moneyman: ""They say money can't buy you happi..."
dialogueTree.english: "They say money can't buy you happiness..."

dialogueTree.title: Moneyman: ""...but that just means you don't h..."
dialogueTree.english: "...but that just means you don't have enough money."
dialogueTree.polish: „...ale to tylko znaczy, że mają pieniędzy za mało”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "...але гэта толькі азначае, што ў іх замала грошай".

dialogueTree.title: Moneyman: ""You have to invest your money wise..."
dialogueTree.english: "You have to invest your money wisely."

dialogueTree.title: Moneyman: ""You can buy stocks with money.""
Moneyman: ""And then use those stocks to make..."
dialogueTree.english: "And then use those stocks to make even more money."
dialogueTree.polish: „A potem z tych udziałów wyciągać jeszcze większe pieniądze”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «А потым з гэтых акцый здабываць яшчэ большыя грошы».

dialogueTree.title: Moneyman: ""That way you'll have enough when y..."
dialogueTree.english: "That way you'll have enough when you grow too old to make new money."
dialogueTree.polish: „W ten sposób zarobisz dość pieniędzy na czas, kiedy będziesz za stary, żeby zarabiać”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Такім чынам вы заробіце дастаткова грошай на той час, калі будзеце занадта старыя, каб зарабляць».

dialogueTree.title: Moneyman: ""Real estate is the graveyard where..."
dialogueTree.english: "Real estate is the graveyard where tired, old money goes to rest."
dialogueTree.polish: „Rynek nieruchomości to taki cmentarz, na którym stara, zmęczona fortuna idzie spocząć”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Рынак нерухомасці — гэта такі могільнік, дзе старая, стомленая фартуна ідзе адпачыць».

dialogueTree.title: Moneyman: ""Money is what literally makes the..."
dialogueTree.english: "Money is what literally makes the world turn."

dialogueTree.title: Moneyman: ""The laws of money are just like th..."
dialogueTree.english: "The laws of money are just like the laws of nature."
dialogueTree.polish: „Pieniędzmi rządzą te same prawa co całym stworzeniem”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «Грошамі кіруюць тыя ж законы, што і ўсім стварэннем».

dialogueTree.title: Moneyman: ""Unpaid labour doesn't net you any..."
dialogueTree.english: "Unpaid labour doesn't net you any money."
dialogueTree.polish: „Praca za darmo nie prowadzi do pieniędzy”.

dialogueTree.title: Moneyman: ""There is no such thing as free mon..."
dialogueTree.english: "There is no such thing as free money."
dialogueTree.polish: „Nie ma czegoś takiego jak pieniądze za darmo”.

dialogueTree.title: Moneyman: ""Money is all about numbers.""
dialogueTree.belarusian: «У грошах галоўным чынам усё зводзіцца да лічбаў».

dialogueTree.title: Moneyman: ""Money is actually all about trust.""
dialogueTree.polish: „W pieniądzach chodzi tak naprawdę głównie o zaufanie”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: «У грашах насамрэч галоўным чынам ідзе гаворка пра давер».
